例如：
print "Enter season: "
season = gets.chomp
case season                          # 在 season 的結構中
when "Spring"                        # 當 season 是 Spring 的時候
    puts "It's spring."             # 印出 It's spring.
when "Summer"                        
   puts "It's summer."
when "Autumn
   puts "It's autumn."
when "Winter"
   puts "It's winter.
else                               # 其他的名字 
  puts "No  #{season} this season"               # No  #{輸入的字串} this season  
end